org.deviceconnect.android.profile

クラス HumanDetectProfile

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.deviceconnect.android.profile.DConnectProfile
      • org.deviceconnect.android.profile.HumanDetectProfile
  • すべての実装されたインタフェース:
    DConnectSpecConstants, org.deviceconnect.profile.DConnectProfileConstants, org.deviceconnect.profile.HumanDetectProfileConstants

    public abstract class HumanDetectProfile
extends DConnectProfile
implements org.deviceconnect.profile.HumanDetectProfileConstants
    Human Detect Profile.

    API that provides Setting, the Detection feature for Human Detect Device.
    DevicePlugin that provides a HumanDetect operation function of for smart device inherits an equivalent class, and implements the corresponding API thing.
